aren\'t going to *be* any significant inter-world linkages in the
Imperium. You may know someone who moved 1 or 2 jumps away. But what
are the odds that an average person will have any sort of "personal"
relationship with someone 5 or 6 jumps away? Even *business*
relationships will be pretty abstract. 

