Having done similar work (although from the programmer, not graphics point 
of view) I am of the opinion that while javascript rollovers and such are 
neat and allow for more attractive sites, they should never be required for 
site operation.

A specific of this is to use the <!-- <SCRIPT> </SCRIPT> --> syntax for 
scripts.

