be as pretty.  Note that this doesn\'t mean multiple versions, just one 
version readable by most.  Techniques like that allow nice looking 4+ pages 
that are work as less attractive 3+ pages.  I don\'t remember the difference 
between 2 and 3, so I\'m not sure that the same can be done there.  The 
policy at my company is that all pages must be usable (if ugly) by 3+ 
browsers....

