we are suppose to
have more female Aslan than males. Then, those males that are not first
born run off and
become Ihatei, "driving their ships to new lands"(Zepplin Rocks!). Does
this not cause a
big depopulation problem? The only fix I can think of is that there must
be an awful lot
of Aslan.

