above placement does sound correct, according to the DGP placement (who made
beautiful Traveller maps, covering the entire Imperium, with exact star placement).

Scangen is in the Commonality of Kedzudh, and I do remember that it is in the Firgr
subsector, directly coreward from the Aramis subsector.  Hex number 2937 sounds
right to me, because I remember looking this planet up for Gvoudzon, the Vargr
character in the Traveller Adventure (I used the planet as part of his background
when we played that campaign).

I would look it up for you, but my Trav stuff is boxed up, at the bottom of a
closet, with several boxes laid on top--and I\'m not sure which of the four Trav
boxes I have include that alien module.

But, as I said, that placement listed above does seem correct.  I remember Scangen
being just over the Imperial border, in Vargr space, and very close to the Spinward
end of the Gvurrdon Sector.

It\'s really not too far from the Aramis subsector at all.

Not exactly what you wanted, but I hope it helps.

Kenneth.
