governmental intrusion on personal affairs and the
greater the level of corruption.  Lower law level
societies therefore provide more formal safeguards to
individuals against the state.

>Is it allowed in Imperial Law courts?

Not in my Traveller Universe, unless the person
asserting the right is a noble.  

