> which to grapple and study on when we attain the stars.

Yep. See some of the ones above. I\'m sure the imams(?) will come up
with *something*. 

> It\'s always nice to meet someone who is conversant in a belief not
> necessarily their own.  Well met, Black ICE.

I\'m not as conversant as I\'d like, but perhaps someday.

Salaam aliekum!

